Upstairs 2-bedroom 1-bathroom unit available from Aug 6th. $3280/month.  <br>
<br>
Pet friendly upstairs remodelled unit with in-unit washer and dryer, and private garage with power door. Walking distance to downtown San Mateo and Caltrain station. Please sign up for open house at https://forms.gle/6VuhR3WjGHHKeHUh6<br>
<br>
- Photo slide show: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SzemaOCWdq8<br>
<br>
- Website: https://sites.google.com/view/439claremont/ <br>
<br>
Centrally located and walking to downtown San Mateo and Burlingame. Easy access to Hwy 101, Caltrain Stations, High Tech and BioTech Companies. Completely and tastefully updated with modern features: granite kitchen and high-end appliances, private laundry, modern bathroom, wood/laminate flooring, and private garage. You can't beat the location or the comfort of this quiet and modern home. <br>
<br>
****** Features of the Unit ******<br>
<br>
The whole-house renovation was just completed with tons of features:<br>
<br>
- Spacious Corner Unit: 1200 sqft of space filled with sunlight from over-sized windows;<br>
<br>
- Heat &amp; Cool Furnishing for optimal comfort: whole-unit central heating, air conditioner, double-pane low-E windows, full-attic R38 insulation;<br>
<br>
- Wood/laminate flooring through the unit and tiles in the kitchen <br>
<br>
- Large Kitchen with Dining Area: granite counter-top, high-end appliances (dishwasher, stove, range fan, refrigerator, disposal), hardwood cabinet with loads of cabinet space, LED lights;<br>
<br>
- In-unit High-end Washer &amp; Dryer; <br>
<br>
- New central air heating system; portable window AC is provided<br>
<br>
- Spacious Bedrooms: This unit has two spacious bedrooms with a lot of natural light.<br>
<br>
- Private Garage: with new garage door and automatic door opener;<br>
<br>
- Electric-car Ready: 110v and 220v dedicated outlets in garage ready to support EV car fast charger.<br>
<br>
- Two Dedicated Parking Spaces: one in private garage and one tandem slot in front of garage. Additional 5 street parkings in front of the building.<br>
<br>
- Front and Back entrance doors: patio/balconies at front and back, brand new wood stairways.<br>
<br>
- Low Cost of Living: No HOA Fee, No Garage &amp; Sewage Fees. Only pay for your own usage with separate utility meters. Brand-new energy efficient windows and high-rating attic insulation.<br>
<br>
****** Location ******<br>
<br>
Neighborhood: <br>
<br>
- The area is ranked among the safest neighborhoods in the nation.<br>
<br>
- Peaceful, scenic neighborhood perfect for walking/running/cycling.<br>
<br>
- Highly desirable San Mateo School District. <br>
<br>
- Walking distance to restaurants, grocery markets, fast-food, gas stations, Starbucks, shopping centers, banks, parks, hospitals, etc. <br>
<br>
- Woodlake Shopping Center featuring Safeway, Starbucks, CVS, Subway, and so much more.<br>
<br>
Commuting:<br>
<br>
- Walking to many bus lines and CalTrain stations.<br>
<br>
- Easy access to El Camino Real, Highway I-101, I-280, 92, etc.<br>
<br>
- 9 minutes to SFO Airport and Millbrae BART. 15 miles either direction to Palo Alto or San Francisco, 30 miles to San Jose. <br>
<br>
- Live close to it all, Oracle, Electronic Arts, GoPro, SolarCity, NetSuite, Genentech, Google, Facebook, and San Francisco! <br>
